      • playWaveFile

        void playWaveFile(String filePath,
                int callId,
                int way)
                  throws RemoteException
        Parameters:
        filePath - filePath the file to play in stream
        callId - the call to play to
        way - the way the file should be played (way & (1<<0)) => send to remote party (micro), (way & (1<<1) ) => send to user (speaker/earpiece) example : way = 3 : will play sound both ways

        RemoteException
